title: Heavy Metal War Realm Of The Wicked
description:
NOW GET READY FOR WAR

----------------------------------------------

A Tale of a magical war in a brutal land
of witches, demons, and warriors. 
The forces of Dark hold sway and only
the bravest, most dedicated Knights Of Metal
can survive to fight their dark powers and
unforgiving, relentless  hate.
Follow the fighting Hordes 
into the very Land of the Dead and Back 
to resurrect the Ragged Mystical Roots 
of Holy Heavy Metal! 
------------------------------------------------

[ Full-length concept album with short narration between tracks]
